</p>
<p>non-United Nations humanitarian organizations working in the protection sector. It is one of several 
</p>
<p>such sectoral clusters. OHCHR leads the Protection Cluster in the Occupied Palestinian Territory. For 
</p>
<p>more information on the cluster system, see www.ochaopt.org/content.aspx?id=1010056. The 
</p>
<p>casualty figures are subject to ongoing verification.  
</p>
