</p>
<p>of a Wall in the Occupied Palestinian Territory (A/ES-10/273 and Corr.1), para. 120; 
</p>
<p>CCPR/C/ISR/CO/4, para. 17.  
</p>
<p> 75 www.un.org/sg/statements/index.asp?nid=8120.  
